item.title: About Youwithouto
item.description: Hi, there! I’m Yu, a.k.a., Youwithouto. I’m currently a Ph.D. candidate at the University of Sydney and my research is mainly about computer-aided hehaviour change. My research interest is pretty broad, including cloud computing, distributed computing, artificial intelligence, deep learning, and human computer interaction. I read a lot and I have been reading book, other people’s blogs, research papers, and other things for a long time, but I’ve never blogged. I’ll try to make a habit of blogging this year and that’s why I created this blog.
